title: X1 genomic DNA from whole blood

data_processing: IDAT files were preprocessed and converted into beta value by minfi Bioconductor package
data_processing.1: Tab-delimited .txt files reporting normalized (SWAN) Average Beta values are linked as supplementary files on the Series record.

scan_protocol: Arrays were imaged using BeadArray Reader using standard recommended Illumina scanner setting
data_processing: IDAT files were preprocessed and converted into beta value by minfi Bioconductor package
data_processing.1: Tab-delimited .txt files reporting normalized (SWAN) Average Beta values are linked as supplementary files on the Series record.
